<h4 id="drive-guide---mt-pisgah-from-green-knob">Drive Guide - Mt Pisgah from Green Knob</h4>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 20 minutes (includes a stop for soft drink at the ‚Äúcountry store‚Äù)</li>
  <li><strong>Seasonal/Limited Access</strong>: Blue Ridge Parkway closed in winter</li>
  <li><strong>Directions</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Head East/North on BRP and go 6.7</li>
      <li>After passing long parking on L, bear R at Buck Spring (paved rd w/grass triangle). Go 0.1</li>
      <li>Drive through first parking to far end of 2nd parking (about 0.3)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

