<h4 id="drive-guide---mt-pisgah-from-atlanta">Drive Guide - Mt Pisgah from Atlanta</h4>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 3:25, 177 miles</li>
  <li><strong>Google Maps</strong> URL from Ashford Dunwoody Rd and I-285 at 33.917, -84.3378:</li>
  <li><strong>Seasonal/Limited Access</strong>: Blue Ridge Parkway closed in winter.   KI4SVM says ‚Äúoften access from the side Hwy 215 is available‚Ä¶ BRP‚Äôs infoline‚Ä¶ is highly recommended - 828-298-0398.‚Äù Check the <a href="http://www.nps.gov/maps/blri/road-closures/">BRP Closure Map</a>.</li>
